   He (Kaiming):   Var(W) = 2/fan_in          — designed for ReLU
   Xavier/Glorot:  Var(W) = 2/(fan_in+fan_out) — designed for sigmoid/tanh
   Keeps activation variance ≈ 1.0 throughout the forward pass

3. Gradient clipping (for exploding):
