  Linear (affine) quantization:
    scale      = (W_max − W_min) / (2^bits − 1)
    zero_point = round(−W_min / scale)
    W_quant    = clamp(round(W / scale + zero_point), 0, 2^bits−1)
    W_dequant  = (W_quant − zero_point) × scale

